Seq1.CallerContent: Hi there, I was wondering if I could make an appointment as a new patient?
Seq1.ReceiverContent: Good morning, thank you for calling Crofton Family Practice. How may I assist you today?

Seq2.ReceiverContent: For the new patients, we will send an email link to your email address and you can register. And the first appointment would be a tele-visit for sure. Will that be okay with you?

Seq3.ReceiverContent: Okay, one moment. Could you spell out your email address?

Seq4.CallerContent: Oh, my email, I'm sorry. It's K-R-O-S-A-T-2-at-gmail.com.

Seq5.ReceiverContent: Okay, I'll repeat again. It's K is Kenneth, R is Randy, O is Oscar, S is Sandra, A is Allison, T is Tommy, 2-at-gmail.com. Am I correct?

Seq6.ReceiverContent: Is there anything else that I may assist you with?

Seq7.ReceiverContent: Okay, thanks for calling Crofton Family Practice and you have a great day.
